+# cr_ordered_channel_parity
+
+This pack gates ordered-channel route-delta facts emitted as `lev.sim_eval.provider_evidence.v1` from the `sim.julia` and `sim.jax` lanes.
+
+`plugins/sim-eval/src/cr-result-adapter.ts` supersedes hand-written wrapper examples for `codex_ratchet.engine_leg_result.v1` JSON. Use the adapter to emit provider evidence, then feed the resulting lane records to this pack.
